spec_data.Name: perl-NetPacket-LLC
spec_data.Description:
NetPacket::LLC provides a set of routines for assembling and disassembling
packets using the IEEE standard LLC protocol layer.

spec_data.Summary: Assemble and disassemble IEEE 802.3 LLC protocol packets
